Earlier this week apparently there was some unusual traffic against
the wiki, and anonymous access has been temporarily suspended, until
we and Atlassian figure out what's going on. In the mean time I made a
copy of the front page here:
https://github.com/internetarchive/heritrix3/wiki

Noah
